50cba2d9f8","tid":2389401,"uid":294342,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"afd2b2022163336f4df5078d38499bbc08c6a30b","tid":2389401,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"0fd3344ddcf7fcea9fbe17ad65bac3e2e6408549","tid":2389401,"uid":388182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e934b93f77bc44dbbcaa79dabc42595c470704f2","tid":2389401,"uid":220431,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"唔洗驚 因為已經衰退緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"係咪要盡早接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"Google Search testosterone replacement therapy<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁撚過哂中藥、所有民間偏方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:18:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>睪固酮替代療法（Testosterone Replacement Therapy, TRT）可能增加男性中風和心臟病發作的風險</strong><br />\n <br />\n一項研究顯示，睪丸激素低的男性使用睪固酮替代療法，特別是在使用的前兩年，罹患缺血性中風、短暫性腦缺血發作（transient ischemic attack, TIA）或心肌梗塞的風險略高。在「美國醫學雜誌」上 的研究結果證實了許多衛生機構對治療相關潛在風險的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n該研究分析了英國醫療保險體系患者電子病歷的大型數據庫，並評估15,401名年齡在45歲(含)以上，睪固酮低（性功能減退）的男性族群。與非使用者相比，睪固酮替代療法的使用者<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">心血管事件風險增加21％</span></span>，相當於額外增加128例事件。但增加的風險似乎是短暫的，在使用睪固酮替代療法兩年後下降。<br />\n<br />\n研究建議臨床醫生在考慮使用睪固酮替代療法時要謹慎行事，並首先討論患者的潛在益處和風險。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章來源: American Journal of Medicine, volume 132, issue 9"},{"pid":"4b8ca68dc30ddf901bf5aad19b9fd846927d8e70","tid":2389401,"uid":42344,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"bde1845b16efd786f658414a12ea8c0b06b4a666","tid":2389401,"uid":34286,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"試下深蹲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eb68f8b2bf3bf65c0c3a73e968675d3df6e923","tid":2389401,"uid":40852,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"返工後已經冇咗<br />\n都叫慳返啲時間<br />\n一朝早唔洗扯住等痾尿"},{"pid":"a059d71bcc5972f207195bc56c3b69f7698bd5cd","tid":2389401,"uid":82929,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1d5a4b67ccb241d8290572b625405650cba2d9f8","tid":2389401,"uid":294342,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"afd2b2022163336f4df5078d38499bbc08c6a30b","tid":2389401,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"0fd3344ddcf7fcea9fbe17ad65bac3e2e6408549","tid":2389401,"uid":388182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"係咪要盡早接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"Google Search testosterone replacement therapy<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁撚過哂中藥、所有民間偏方"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:18:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>睪固酮替代療法（Testosterone Replacement Therapy, TRT）可能增加男性中風和心臟病發作的風險</strong><br />\n <br />\n一項研究顯示，睪丸激素低的男性使用睪固酮替代療法，特別是在使用的前兩年，罹患缺血性中風、短暫性腦缺血發作（transient ischemic attack, TIA）或心肌梗塞的風險略高。在「美國醫學雜誌」上 的研究結果證實了許多衛生機構對治療相關潛在風險的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n該研究分析了英國醫療保險體系患者電子病歷的大型數據庫，並評估15,401名年齡在45歲(含)以上，睪固酮低（性功能減退）的男性族群。與非使用者相比，睪固酮替代療法的使用者<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">心血管事件風險增加21％</span></span>，相當於額外增加128例事件。但增加的風險似乎是短暫的，在使用睪固酮替代療法兩年後下降。<br />\n<br />\n研究建議臨床醫生在考慮使用睪固酮替代療法時要謹慎行事，並首先討論患者的潛在益處和風險。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章來源: American Journal of Medicine, volume 132, issue 9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"風險就樓主自己諗啦<br />\n低T冇性欲、冇動力、生不如死<br />\nTrT低機率早死幾10年"},{"pid":"ab8f49b570ef1694fdac0504f9270ca1665eb686","tid":2389401,"uid":328862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd33499004aa1e0d8c1bc6d57fca9c8e4eb12dda","tid":2389401,"uid":388182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"對D女女無哂興趣咁,個人對所以野都無咩熱誠,點搞........."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"之前有食藥個陣完全唔會起頭<br />\n依家停左藥 <br />\n朝朝晨勃到痛醒<br />\n<br />\n利申: 藥娘"},{"pid":"ca911c2325ed9e5a0f3181a71db48e143cb02c7f","tid":2389401,"uid":100623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b56ff9693f8bac60a1979c3fd41ea1064de0463","tid":2389401,"uid":78546,"like":945,"dislike":7,"score":938,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T01:12:20.000Z","msg":"因為依個年齡個身體預左人有幫你含醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0ede34fd1097b9577e31677eae1d47c1d7c82c","tid":2389401,"uid":43095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5b339743d5e51cd5f6d62e34f9b0a1dca529283","tid":2389401,"uid":134908,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4002cc419685b1359c5cb7e24132d08ab531251","tid":2389401,"uid":139863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"j得太多"},{"pid":"9b90ebb2855a7f2037b3b258c0cdd69b56a33d5e","tid":2389401,"uid":63618,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score